data.description: This move-in ready 2 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage home in the heart of Spring Hill is looking for it's new owner!  Open Floor Plan with an amazing window seat with Plantation Shutters to give it ertra style.  Kitchen Island doubles as a Breakfast Bar  with a window overlooking an amazing back yard. there is plenty of counter space in the kitchen, along with an abundance of wooden cabinets, Stainless steel appliances, and cozy dinette area!  Appliances are less than 2 years old.  High ceilings throughout give the house that spacious feeling.Master bedroom suite is sizable, and has an enormous walk-in closet with shelves. Guest bedroom is spacious with 4 closets, plus its own entrance into the backyard! French Doors lead out to the enclosed Florida room that  could be utilized as a home office, workout room, game room, or just sit and relax with a cup of coffee and a good book while you unwind from a long day.Large screened in covered porch.   Red, barn-style shed in the back would make an excellent workshop or creative space, and has plenty of room for storage. Laminate flooring, carpeting and ceramic tile through-out. Prime location in a pleasant neighborhood, minutes away from shopping, entertainment, and local restaurants! Close to the Veteran's expressway for easy access to downtown Tampa. Hot water heater installed in 2004, roof replaced in 2009, and the compressor in the A/C unit was replaced in 2010. You can park your RV or Boat in your back yard. Beautiful Palm Trees in the front yard give you that feel of privacy. Property is fenced on 3 sides.  Mature Landscaping with that Florida style in the large back yard which is hard to find in the heart of Spring Hill!  Plenty of room to add a pool.  Make your appointment to see this home today BEFORE IT'S GONE!
